            <h1 class="study-title">Proverbs 17</h1>
            <p class="study-subtitle">KJV &bull; YLT &bull; ASV &bull; WEB &mdash; <a href="../interlinear/pro-17.html" style="color:var(--ultramarine);">View Interlinear &rarr;</a></p>
